Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.03,0:33:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention the the burning wire is\Ngoing through your body and good god. Uh
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.44,0:33:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll give you just a taste of it. So\Nit it is um so the Buddha is the is the
