Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.72,0:34:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In that lifetime I was a hinana\NBuddhist. So I'll tell you that and then
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.04,0:34:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that's another story. But in the\Nprevious lifetime, I was a Hinyana
