Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.28,0:34:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,general. Mahayana Hinana. Anyway, my\Nbelief system
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.48,0:35:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,um my belief system and I meditated for\Nmany years uh was that uh the ultimate
