Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.32,0:35:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,uh the infinite reality is allness\Nversus uh nothingness is comes up over
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.04,0:35:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,900 910 about 900 by 900 would discern\Nonce you pass that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.96,0:35:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,all right so many of those schools of\NBuddhism were below 900 so they confuse
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.28,0:35:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,all nothingness and void\NI was very
