Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.88,0:36:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh the reality the ultimate reality\Nwas void.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.35,0:36:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went out of body went into the\Nvoid, there was a number of lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.64,0:36:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,where there's no connection between the\Nlifetimes. There was awareness, blank
