Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.92,0:36:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness of existence came out of\Nnothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.83,0:36:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H\Nfrom nothingness existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.44,0:36:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then it all solved itself. Each\Ntime I went out of body
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.83,0:36:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in that form of Buddhism where the\Nultimate reality was void, I I
