Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.76,0:36:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But after many lifetimes, a powerful\Nmeditation upon that truth, I created
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:37:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,voidness as.\NAnd today there are mistransations of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.48,0:37:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the teachings of the Buddha. Not\Nmistransations but it's not explained in
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.52,0:37:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a way that would help you to avoid this\Nerror.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.11,0:37:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My own profound belief that the ultimate\Nreality my devotion to Buddha was such
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.64,0:37:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that I went into nothingness every time\NI went out of body. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.00,0:37:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, because that's not a reality.\NYou can't stay in void as nothingness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.20,0:37:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,void. You can't stay there. It's not a\Nreality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.80,0:37:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, you find yourself back in\Nanother body. Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.07,0:37:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a sudden explosion when I hit\Nback this body. There's a little wagon
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.32,0:37:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and this body me called me in those days\Nage three or four sitting in this wagon
