Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.72,0:39:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um what was I saying?\N>> Conflict with Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.07,0:39:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh yeah, Jesus and Buddha. Um so it was\Na conflict. I had a teacher who had at
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.16,0:40:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one time been in a very high state. I\Nhad not realized was not in such a high
