Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.35,0:40:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,etc. and said those are all attachments\Nyou should release on those attachments.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.64,0:40:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Those are all the attributes of\NGod. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.92,0:40:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that came out of that same\NBuddhist uh tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.72,0:40:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Love and the attachment to love are two\Ndifferent things. I didn't realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.00,0:40:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, at the time I said, "Yes,\Nlove is an attachment." He's telling me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.04,0:40:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let go on beauty, love, all that\Nstuff."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.72,0:40:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's looking on it down on as an\Nattachment. I was in conflict between
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.16,0:40:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus and Buddha. So, I had the\Nmisunderstanding of Buddha as
