Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.72,0:41:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,finally I said no Buddha is higher than\NJesus. Love is attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.56,0:41:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I started releasing on love.\NI went into the infinite void.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.11,0:41:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This time not unconsciously\Nconsciously went into the void. And I'll
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.20,0:41:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,tell you the void is very very\Nimpressive. It is very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.20,0:41:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a dimension\Nthat is beyond some puny little eagle.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.48,0:41:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you the absolute\Nexperience of nothingness. Infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.56,0:41:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,nothingness.\NThere was one thought left.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.00,0:41:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In it all reality is revealed. You see\Neverything moving of its own nature
