Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.56,0:42:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So it does reveal\Nreality starkly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.64,0:42:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was something wrong.\NSome innate spiritual intuition of its
