Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.31,0:43:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as a paper boy when I had all I was\Nfrozen to death you know I went into a
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.68,0:43:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,divine space and the most profound thing\Nof it beyond all time beyond all you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.35,0:43:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,realize\Nthat that you always existed before all
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.72,0:43:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,universes I am and after all universes\Nhave gone I will still prevail that's
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.11,0:44:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for sure\Nuniverses are just nothing you know that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.00,0:44:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in that space but the most profound\Nthing is like an enormous love of such a
