Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.92,0:44:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,answers the difference between salvation\Nand enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.80,0:44:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite reality as allness rather\Nthan voidness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.76,0:44:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The void means void of all form. Void of\Nall form because that which you are is
