Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.28,1:00:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightened. Okay. Looks like\Nnow this is a very simple thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.96,1:00:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All the stuff you read about and what\Nmost of the world follows is
