Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.31,1:00:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,heights in those years. It was\Nterrifying. Just a bunch of damn stones
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.24,1:00:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and these beautiful llamas around.\NAnd I got home uh and now I got llamas.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.55,1:00:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Nwhen I got out of Machu Picchu was
