Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.20,1:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do a llama.\N>> Oh, llamas.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.40,1:00:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Uh I'm thinking of our llamas at home.\NUh we have permission. resist. They
