Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.79,1:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody just you all back off and\Nif you don't back off she spits at Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.76,1:02:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh golly.\NWell, the discovery that animals are
