Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.83,1:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with a a drive to realize\Nthe truth. Um
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.79,1:06:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the teachings of the Buddha are of\Ncourse the traditional the ancient vidas
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.92,1:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,have uh uh profound truth.\NYou try to find something that there's
