Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.03,1:07:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a number of teachers in the\N700s who I respect and uh refer to.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.68,1:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Their teachings are cryptic. Uh\Nthere's no explanation. So that um you
